Detailed Description

Parameters:
P Required argument. Device prefix
Q Required argument. Device suffix
PORT Required argument. Asyn port and object name
NELM Default=100000. Maximum number of elements in position compare array
EMPTY Default=. Empty macro to satisfy VDCT
PREC Default=4. Precision to show position compare gate and pulse fields
M1 Default=:NOMOTOR. Motor 1 PV
M1DIR Default=+. Set to - if motor inverted in geobrick (decode control = 3 instead of 7)
M2 Default=:NOMOTOR. Motor 2 PV
M2DIR Default=+. Set to - if motor inverted in geobrick (decode control = 3 instead of 7)
M3 Default=:NOMOTOR. Motor 3 PV
M3DIR Default=+. Set to - if motor inverted in geobrick (decode control = 3 instead of 7)
M4 Default=:NOMOTOR. Motor 4 PV
M4DIR Default=+. Set to - if motor inverted in geobrick (decode control = 3 instead of 7)
